{
  "stem": "8610.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I did three days work in the fields, three days work in the office, and one day, a Saturday, in my synagogue until I was commissioned.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then once being commissioned, I was given a-- my first posting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Again, was to a, a training camp where former refugees from Germany were serving in the army, a place called Richborough Camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was with them for quite a while until I was sent overseas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In 1941, I went overseas to the Middle East.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was there for three years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I became senior chaplain for the Middle East forces, having a delightful parish stretching from Turkey to Tunisia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That covered Lebanon, Syria, Palestine, Transjordan, North Africa, right up to Tunisia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So it was quite an experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And whilst there, of course-- 1941 to 1944-- we were getting news of what was happening in Europe, particularly with our Palestinian Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I had 25,000 Hebrew-speaking Palestinian Jews serving in the British Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And many of them were-- had relatives in Europe, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So we were very conscious of, of what the situation was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, and this-- the antagonism to Germany became very intense.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that is why so many of these Palestinian Jews were anxious to get into the battle, as it were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they were very frustrated that they weren't sent into the field.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Until the early part of 1944, when the independent Jewish Brigade was formed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they went out-- trained in, in Africa, went over to Italy, and were involved in the last stages of the war in Europe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1937.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The community didn't mind because it had-- it's a job that had to be done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the army needed Jewish chaplains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My wife, well-- throughout the whole of our life, she's had to bear the brunt.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
